name: Lich of the Wood.
description:
.... "Incredible! I can't believe it. You've renamed the tavern!? painted and everything. Overnight as well. I'm dumbfounded. Is Ambrose around? I have to speak with him about this."

Barmaid: "umm. yes, sure. I suppose it does feel a bit fresh this morning, but I'm positive we've had this name ever since I can remember. And I'm afraid I don't know Ambrose"

.... "Don't know him? Well then who hired you? Look I've had a hell of a day, just go in the back and ask for him, he's always in about this hour"

Barmaid: " Sir, are you alright? You look tired... You didn't come from the wood did you? You weren't in the forest right? Sir, what's your name?

.... "My name... huh.... well that's a funny thing innit. Just go fetch Ambrose. Please. I know he's about. Please"
